text: Yuliya Buyeva (born December 24, 1975) is a Ukrainian volleyball player. She represented Ukraine during the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta. She played for Universidad Granada, BBSC Berlin, Beşiktaş, and Universidad de Burgos. == References == == Other websites == * * * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Ukrainian volleyball players
